      "content": "i know they love me, but love doesnt make it any easier to watch them exhaust themselves trying to take care of me. i feel like i'm just taking up space and energy that they could be using for their own lives. sometimes i think if i wasn't around, everything would just... be easier for them. they'd finally have their freedom back without all this constant worry about me.",
