      "content": "it just feels selfish to keep holding on when i can see how much i'm slowing them down. i just want them to be happy and free. do you think it's really wrong to want to just... stop being a problem for them? i feel like if i just slipped away quietly, it would be a gift to them instead of a tragedy.",
